OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge pothole fund to
OL,4,Cfix 'sorry state' of Scotland's roads
OL,6,FScottish Labour has pledged to fix the
OL,7,F"sorry state" of Scotland's roads with
OL,8,Fa designated pothole fund.
OL,10,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar has
OL,11,Fsaid the party would establish a new
OL,12,Froad repair fund worth #350 million
OL,13,Fover the next five years, enough to
OL,14,Ffix an estimated 4.8 million potholes.
OL,16,FThe party has said councils have had
OL,17,Fto pay out #4.2 million in
OL,18,Fcompensation between 2019/20 and 2023/
OL,19,F24 for damage caused by potholes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@MO]
