OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge pothole fund to
OL,4,Cfix 'sorry state' of Scotland's roads
OL,6,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,7,Fsaid: "Scotland needs change after 20
OL,8,Fyears of SNP government.
OL,10,F"Across Scotland, motorists are paying
OL,11,Fthe price for the SNP's failure to get
OL,12,Fthe basics right.
OL,14,F"Our roads are in a sorry state,
OL,15,Fpotholes are causing misery every
OL,16,Fsingle day, and drivers, families and
OL,17,Fbusinesses are left to pick up the
OL,18,Fbill."
OL,26,@oD@GOUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@FO]
