OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge pothole fund to
OL,4,Cfix 'sorry state' of Scotland's roads
OL,6,FThe funding would be repurposed from
OL,7,Fthe active and sustainable travel
OL,8,Fbudget, while protecting bus
OL,9,Finfrastructure investment.
OL,11,FScottish Labour has pledged more
OL,12,Fpreventative maintenance to improve
OL,13,Froad conditions in the long term.
OL,15,FThe party has previously revealed that
OL,16,Fspending on local roads has fallen by
OL,17,F13% since 2010-11 because of SNP cuts
OL,18,Fto council budgets.
OL,20,FMr Sarwar continued: "This is what 20
OL,21,Fyears of SNP government looks like.
OL,26,@|D@VOU
