OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge pothole fund to
OL,4,Cfix 'sorry state' of Scotland's roads
OL,6,F"Crumbling roads, rising repair costs
OL,7,Fand a government that has turned its
OL,8,Fback on motorists.
OL,10,F"I'm standing to fix the mess, get the
OL,11,Fbasics right and build a better future
OL,12,Ffor Scotland.
OL,14,F"That means fixing the mess the SNP
OL,15,Fhave made of our roads and ending
OL,16,Ftheir war on motorists.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
