OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge pothole fund to
OL,4,Cfix 'sorry state' of Scotland's roads
OL,6,F"A Scottish Labour government will
OL,7,Finvest #350 million to repair nearly
OL,8,Ffive million potholes and make our
OL,9,Froads safer for everyone who relies on
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"On May 7, vote Scottish Labour on
OL,13,Fboth votes to fix the roads and
OL,14,Fdeliver the change Scotland needs."
OL,16,FSNP candidate for Paisley, George Adam
OL,17,Fsaid: "The only people conducting a
OL,18,Fwar on motorists is the Labour UK
OL,19,FGovernment who are refusing to lift a
OL,20,Ffinger to cut fuel duty.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@cO]yD@GOU
