OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775537898
OL,3,CScottish Labour pledge pothole fund to
OL,4,Cfix 'sorry state' of Scotland's roads
OL,6,F"The Labour Party has been asleep at
OL,7,Fthe wheel in letting petrol prices
OL,8,Fsoar and pumps run dry with Anas
OL,9,FSarwar remaining silent as his London
OL,10,Fbosses stand by and do absolutely
OL,11,Fnothing to help Scottish motorists.
OL,13,F"The SNP is clear, if Keir Starmer's
OL,14,FGovernment won't act to bring bills
OL,15,Fdown it should get out of the road and
OL,16,Fhand the powers over to an SNP
OL,17,FScottish Government that will."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@_O]
